# Hard Banned Patterns

## Styling
- NEVER: border-l-4 or border-r-4 with a color class on card components
- NEVER: background gradient on buttons (bg-gradient-*)
- NEVER: inline style={{ color: '#hex' }} — use Tailwind
- NEVER: backdrop-filter on ReactFlow node components
- NEVER: text-purple-* or bg-purple-* for decorative elements (purple = review status only)
- NEVER: hardcode font-size in px via style= — use text-body-md etc tokens

## Architecture  
- NEVER: import server/ code into src/ components
- NEVER: define ReactFlow nodeTypes/edgeTypes inline in JSX
- NEVER: call CPM algorithm from a React component — call from store action
- NEVER: store canvas node positions in React state — use Zustand canvas store
- NEVER: use localStorage or sessionStorage for canvas state — use Zustand + DB sync
- NEVER: put chart components (Recharts) inside canvas/ components
- NEVER: import Material Symbols — use Lucide icons exclusively

## Data
- NEVER: mutate nodes array directly — use setNodes with functional update
- NEVER: derive workload from task array in render — use precomputed store value  
- NEVER: run CPM algorithm synchronously in WebSocket handler — use queue + broadcast

## UX
- NEVER: open a full-page navigation from canvas interaction — use panels/sheets
- NEVER: show a toast for critical errors — use inline error states
- NEVER: create a modal for task creation — use inline canvas node placement
